trans-unit.source: Defines an abstract base class for composable part definitions, which describe and enable the creation of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Define uma classe base abstrata para definições de parte de composição, que descrevem e permitem a criação de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of a part that the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância de uma parte que o <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> descreve.

trans-unit.source: Derived types that override this method should return a new instance of a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object every time that the method is invoked and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Tipos derivados que substituem este método devem retornar uma nova instância de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objeto toda vez que o método é chamado e nunca deve retornar `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the objects exported by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> objetos que descrevem os objetos exportados pela parte definido por este <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade nunca devem retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not provide exported objects, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objetos criados pelo <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>não fornecer objetos exportados, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>coleção em vez disso.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the exported objects provided by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> objetos que descrevem os objetos exportados fornecidos pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objetos criados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objetos que descrevem as importações exigidas pela parte definido por este <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade nunca devem retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objetos criados pelo <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>não tiver importações, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>coleção em vez disso.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objetos que descrevem as importações exigidas pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objetos criados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the metadata for this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de metadados para este <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade devem retornar somente leitura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>objeto com uma comparação não linguística, diferencia maiusculas de minúsculas, como <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>e nunca deve retornar `null`.</xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>não contém metadados, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>objeto em vez disso.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the metadata for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção que contém os metadados para o <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é vazio, somente leitura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objeto.
